text.tspan: Experienced horn players wanted for https://extraextrabrassband.com/ (Flagstaff)
Are you interested to play paid gigs downtown in a fun brass band?
We are a local brass band, since 2021, playing recent pop covers and classics.
If you can play by ear, read charts and/or memorize horn lines of easy pop songs,
we would like to bring you in for an audition!
We get together and play about once per week, either
3. playing gigs at various places nearby (Orpheum, bars, Art in the Park, etc)
